OL,3,CResidents told to avoid the area after
OL,4,Clarge fire at mill in Middleton
OL,6,FTeams of firefighters have tackled a
OL,7,Fhuge blaze at a mill in Greater
OL,8,FManchester.
OL,10,FThe fire in Middleton town centre
OL,11,Fclosed surrounding roads and has
OL,12,Fforced Middleton Arena to shut for the
OL,13,Fday.
OL,15,FIt is understood that the blaze
OL,16,Fstarted at Lodge Mill off Townley
OL,17,FStreet, near its junction with Old
OL,18,FHall Street.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
