OL,3,CResidents told to avoid the area after
OL,4,Clarge fire at mill in Middleton
OL,6,FGreater Manchester Fire and Rescue
OL,7,FService said firefighters were called
OL,8,Fto the scene shortly before 6am on
OL,9,FSunday 29 March with residents
OL,10,Freporting they heard a series of loud
OL,11,Fbangs and "explosions".
OL,13,FThe fire is the latest blaze to hit
OL,14,Fsome of the old mill buildings in the
OL,15,Farea.
OL,17,FPart of Lodge Mill, thought to be the
OL,18,Foldest remaining mill in Middleton,
OL,19,Fwas engulfed by fire in December 2021.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
